# README.HACKING

Describes how to make changes to this module.

## Version Updates

    - Update Changes file
    - Update version number
        - $VERSION in lib/File/Edit.pm
    - Update the README
        - perldoc -t File::Edit > README
    - Build tarball
        - perl Makefile.PL; make test; make dist; make clean
    - Upload latest tarball to CPAN

